<p>The Snow Music app I developed with Ensemble Evolution as part of my research in Piteå, is now available for free on the <a href="http://itunes.apple.com/us/app/snow-music/id560849530?ls=1&amp;mt=8">iTunes store</a>!</p>

<p>Download it and check it out! Leave me a note in the comments/twitter/facebook if you like it.</p>

<p>The app was developed using field recordings from Piteå with Pure Data and libpd, there’s more information about it in my <a href="http://charlesmartin.com.au/2012/6/26/mobile-computer-music-for-percussionists.html">thesis</a> or this <a href="http://charlesmartin.com.au/2012/7/17/paper-in-acmc-2012.html">paper</a>.</p>

<p>Here’s a short video of Ensemble Evolution performing with the app:</p>

